N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 73.5 - Fees

State Regulations
(a) A charge will
be made of 25 cents per photocopy of pages not larger than 81/2 by 14
inches. (b) Charges for materials
or services not specified by statute or regulation shall be based on the actual
cost thereof to the board. (c) Payment for information services should be made by cash or check or money
order, payable to the New York State Department of Labor. Notes
